<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSBITES: THEY'LL COOK FOR THE KIDS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ANNE MICHAUD, Anne Michaud is a staff writer for The Times Orange County 
Edition. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 More than 130 amateur chefs -- all men -- will vie for medals Sunday as they 
cook for charity in the second annual Gourmet Guys contest. Last year, the 
event raised $32,000 for the Children's Museum at La Habra. 
</P>
