<TEXT>
<P>
 A man who died after being stabbed in the throat during an argument has been 
identified as 25-year-old Lorenzo Herrera, but his assailant remains at large, 
police said Wednesday. 
</P>
<P>
 Herrera, a resident of Anaheim, was stabbed in an alley about 3 p.m. Tuesday 
