 Residents of an apartment complex near where the stabbing occurred said both 
men frequented the complex, where they have a friend. Apartment manager Bobbie 
Norton said neither man lived there. 
</P>
<P>
 "From what I understand, they were fighting over a Walkman radio," Norton 
said. "This whole thing has made us all a little nervous. We've been up all 
night." 
