<P>
 Bosnian Serbs on Wednesday accused the Muslim-led government of launching a 
new artillery attack on Brcko in northern Bosnia, 24 hours after shelling 
killed four in the town center, sharply raising tensions in the region. 
</P>
<P>
 But in central and southern Bosnia, Muslim and Croatian leaders agreed on 
political and territorial issues of a Bosnian federation. 
