BEHIND THE SCENES / ORANGE COUNTY: A SMILE MAKES A GREAT ACCESSORY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "Laughter Is Inner Jogging" was the catch phrase for the Wellness Community of 
Orange County's fund-raiser Monday at the Improv in Irvine. But no one chose to 
wear jogging attire . . . thank goodness, although it was OKd on the 
invitation. 
</P>
<P>
 Instead, most of the 270 guests wore business suits or after-6 dresses to the 
fifth annual "Evening at the Improv," a benefit for the organization that 
offers free help to those affected by cancer. 
</P>
