<P>
 Winners Entertainment Inc.: The provider of video game machines said that a 
West Virginia referendum Tuesday on whether to allow electronic gambling at 
horse racetracks passed by a wide margin. 
</P>
<P>
 In the referendum, 80% of the voters approved the machines, which offer 
