<P>
 Winners Entertainment in San Juan Capistrano has operated video gambling 
machines at the Mountaineer Racetrack & Resort in Hancock County, W.Va., for 
almost four years. But for the past year, it has been fending off efforts to 
have the machines banned from the state. 
</P>
<P>
 The company continued to operate the video gambling machines under a temporary 
court order until voters had a chance to decide the issue. 
</P>
</TEXT>
