</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Lincoln Middle School in Santa Monica is among 26 middle and high schools in 
Los Angeles County recognized as a California Distinguished School. 
</P>
<P>
 The only Westside school so honored, Lincoln was compared with 200 California 
middle school applicants. Statewide, 76 middle schools were named distinguished 
schools. 
