<TEXT>
<P>
 The Atlantic Crossing Theatre Project is auditioning young technicians, 
actors, singers, dancers and musicians from 14 to 18 at 9:30 a.m. Saturday at 
Windward School Theatre, 11350 Palms Blvd. in West Los Angeles. 
</P>
<P>
