district's $69-million spending plan showed that ABC will have a budget deficit 
of $2.8 million in the next fiscal year. 
</P>
<P>
 The advisers, who have the authority to overrule the district's spending 
decisions, last month rescinded the ABC board's approval of a teachers' 
contract that includes a 1% salary bonus and reduced class sizes. 
