<P>
 The ABC Unified school board is scheduled Tuesday to consider testing a 
uniform dress code at five elementary schools in Cerritos and Artesia beginning 
in September. 
</P>
<P>
 Parents at the five schools overwhelmingly favor a uniform dress code on 
campus, a recent survey found. 
</P>
<P>
