home in March said they favored the proposal to have the students wear uniforms 
in shades of gray, navy or plaid, school officials said. The survey was sent 
home with students at Burbank, Kennedy and Niemes elementary schools in 
Artesia, and Carver and Nixon elementary schools in Cerritos. 
