<TEXT>
<P>
 Award -- Buck Barker, owner of the Munch Box hamburger stand in Chatsworth, 
will receive a certificate of recognition for service to the community from the 
Chatsworth Coordinating Council later this month. The Times erroneously 
reported Tuesday which award he would receive. 
</P>
