<TEXT>
<P>
 Nakano quote -- Torrance Councilman George Nakano was incorrectly quoted in a 
May 5 South Bay section story about his bid to unseat state Sen. Ralph C. Dills 
(D-Gardena). The quote should have read: "If someone took a strong stand for 
women's rights, does that mean a woman shouldn't be able to run against them?" 
</P>
