<TEXT>
<P>
 Turner's neighbor -- A story in the South Bay edition of The Times May 5 
incorrectly stated that Johnathon Marzet, associated with Turner's Technical 
Institute Inc., is a neighbor of Priscilla Turner, the organization's 
president. Marzet and Turner are not neighbors. 
</P>
